00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:52,930
is a bit more complicated.

197
00:15:52,930 --> 00:15:56,860
I'd rather not get into it now.

198
00:15:56,860 --> 00:16:01,450
So let's leave it here, in
which we don't have time.

