599
00:45:48,030 --> 00:45:56,910
The ratio of the spin orbit
coupling to the ground state

600
00:45:56,910 --> 00:46:00,850
energy is 1 over alpha squared.

601
00:46:00,850 --> 00:46:05,310
It's alpha squared, which
